The paper focuses on adversarial attacks on video recognition models, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The paper also discusses the use of partition-based rectifications, which is related to multimedia (cs.MM) and cryptography and security (cs.CR) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper utilizes deep neural networks, which is a common topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-category.
